'''Cory J. Herndon''' was a [[Court Archivist]] of [[Velmor/Legends|Velmor]] during the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. He was the author of ''[[Velmor: Royalty and Rebellion]]'', a compilation of historical documents. He also cataloged "[[Arbra: Sanctuary In the Storm|Arbra: Sanctuary in the Storm]]."

==Behind the scenes==
Cory Herndon was named after the out-of-universe author of ''Velmor: Royalty and Rebellion'', [[Cory J. Herndon]]. In [[Carida: Heavy Duty]], the character is identified for the first time as Cory J. Herndon.

